From: Sebastian Rasmussen <sebras@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 26 Aug 2018 15:16:46 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] Bug 699673: jbig2dec: Initialize return code for all cases.

Thanks to oss-fuzz for reporting.
---
 jbig2_arith.c | 4 +++-
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/jbig2_arith.c b/jbig2_arith.c
index 58dcff2..d34d792 100644
--- a/jbig2_arith.c
+++ b/jbig2_arith.c
@@ -298,8 +298,10 @@ jbig2_arith_decode(Jbig2ArithState *as, Jbig2ArithCx *pcx, int *code)
             jbig2_arith_renormd(as);
             *code = 0;
             return D;
-        } else
+        } else {
+            *code = 0;
             return cx >> 7;
+        }
     } else {
 #ifdef SOFTWARE_CONVENTION
         as->C -= (as->A) << 16;
